predictor of increased all-cause mortality (hazard ratio 1.49; 95% CI
1.02-2.16, p = 0.037), as determined using Cox regression analysis.
Conclusion: Functional performance was associated with clinical
variables and all-cause mortality in HD patients. (C) 2018 S. Karger AG,
